As a user,
So I can have my own feed to store memories,
I would like to be able to sign up

As a user,
So I can store some of my memories
I would like to be able to upload photos

As a user,
So I can recall my memories
I would like to be able to see a list of my photos in a feed

As a user,
So I can live vicariously
I would like to see the public feeds of others

As a user,
So I can exaggerate my memories
I would like to be able to add filters to my photos

As a user,
So I can show people who I am
I would like to have an avatar that appears alongside my feed

As a user,
So I can add details about my memories
I would like to be able to add a text description alongside each photo

As a user,
So I can express my enjoyment of any photo
I would like to be able to 'like' it

As a user,
So I can express a more detailed opinion on any photo
I would like to be able to comment on it
